{"tid":294143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"已經唔識處理同女朋友之間錢銀上嘅關係","createTime":"2017-06-22T16:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T02:40:07.000Z","uid":16462,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf86ac1c20f952f24cbae670b9c5a4ece8f53a33","tid":294143,"uid":16462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"有個敗家女朋友 一齊左四年半<br />\n平時出街洗費九成我比 開頭一兩年都冇問題好地地<br />\n之前去旅行一齊草左一舊錢<br />\n大部份都係我草 我6/7 佢4/3<br />\n去完旅行之後仲有大概10k淨<br />\n之後問返佢舊錢去左邊 <br />\n佢話佢用咗 仲同我講佢都有份草<br />\n我唔想煩 因為呢件事都好耐之前 咁由佢啦<br />\n咁最近呢一年 佢又join左啲唔知乜鳩美容plan<br />\n咁我同佢講你自己cover到就冇問題啦 <br />\n因為嗰時佢有做野 咁我唔理啦 <br />\n咁佢頭幾個月經濟都無問題 <br />\n直到佢resign前幾個月 <br />\n個個月都唔夠錢用要問我借 <br />\n過咗幾個月之後差唔多年尾 <br />\n又話番工好唔開心好多人事上嘅是非 <br />\n咁我叫佢頂多幾個月做埋年尾 拎埋雙糧花紅先啦 <br />\n佢話佢稀罕 之後就冇做嘢幾個月 <br />\n佢期期數我幫佢孭<br />\n我個個月都冇錢淨 <br />\n直到早兩個月 因為我冇睇牙醫嘅習慣<br />\n牙痛睇牙醫 蛀咗兩隻啊 要杜牙根 9k <br />\n嗰個月我要問老豆借錢睇牙醫 連家用都無比<br />\n我自從出嚟做嘢之後 冇拎過屋企錢 個個月準時俾家用<br />\n個感覺好奇怪 <br />\n到而家條八婆有番工 佢自己啲數自己孭番<br />\n到呢個時候 我已經比咗大概30k佢<br />\n早一個月 八婆話借我信用話買幾十蚊野 咁我check返啲記錄 日日都用我信用卡幾百幾百蚊咁用 最後比我發現佢去貨金 最後課左4k 比我屌到仆街先識收手<br />\n我已經唔識得處理我哋之間錢銀上嘅關係<br />\nSorry 1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85423296c91d47d4362679d56575045afafe1811","tid":294143,"uid":28792,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"你條女係心理有問題<br />\n唔係你唔識處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3215e0c0a5958e139b99370e30c0f87e611b22e5","tid":294143,"uid":81347,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"屌到佢還錢 然後分手 完"},{"pid":"fe76f84776bc406fa6e8b4b47bdca35d2c584748","tid":294143,"uid":82398,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"我有俾你屌架"},{"pid":"0d390ef56de88eb1c95014479ae6eee41bab9332","tid":294143,"uid":1706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"屌，分手擺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5fa961c116bebc1e0f6f1dee2dfadd0c17d8ca","tid":294143,"uid":70962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"睇你覺得值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113f0c2a77a33340bad7bdd11feae848ec268200","tid":294143,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://download.ithome.com.tw/uploads/image-upload/51ef339356bdd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdownload.ithome.com.tw%2Fuploads%2Fimage-upload%2F51ef339356bdd.gif&h=e4fb98ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b902498cabe871833817d1bef3d196c1870b30a0","tid":294143,"uid":12437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"分手啦，當你係水魚"},{"pid":"44414da2a98825cb60135ec939afd4b843deb5b9","tid":294143,"uid":3180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:05:15.000Z","msg":"我都敗家，不過我啲數自己孭返，一路都無同人借<br />\n樓主快啲cut卡啦，一陣佢抄底你啲卡資料就無底洞<br />\n絕情啲既可以報警"},{"pid":"6bce23dab0fb4255bf9c1bb7f466db80192d2a83","tid":294143,"uid":37623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:05:18.000Z","msg":"飛左佢啦"},{"pid":"66b84aa4add5d033407dc32cf50f67ae941b9e4a","tid":294143,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"似有心理病<br />\n<br />\n但從行為睇得出幾無恥<br />\n而同無恥既女仔一齊通常都無好下場<br />\n飛左佢比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de4d45a5a74ae7237e4f0a261301314ebd44847","tid":294143,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"講錢傷感情<br />\n樓主早走早著"},{"pid":"91cc5f877268ec082ad4920a6e4a90972fb54429","tid":294143,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB